{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_001", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子是一种常见的柑橘类水果，果肉多汁，味道酸甜，带有明显的清香。", "citation_locator": "line:5;section:1. 概述;paragraph:1", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_002", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子既可以直接剥皮食用，也可以榨成果汁，还可以用于制作甜点、果酱和沙拉。", "citation_locator": "line:5;section:1. 概述;paragraph:1", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_003", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子的特点包括：水分充足，口感清爽；酸甜适中，香气明显；富含维生素 C；适合作为饭后水果或日常加餐；可直接食用，也适合榨汁和制作饮品。", "citation_locator": "line:9;section:1. 概述;paragraph:3", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_004", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子最突出的营养特点是含有较多维生素 C，同时也含有水分、膳食纤维和一些植物化合物。", "citation_locator": "line:17;section:2. 主要营养特点;paragraph:4", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_005", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "维生素 C 是人体需要的重要营养素之一，日常饮食中可以通过水果和蔬菜获取。", "citation_locator": "line:21;section:2.1 维生素 C;paragraph:5", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_006", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "相比苹果、香蕉等水果，橙子的维生素 C 含量通常更有优势。", "citation_locator": "line:23;section:2.1 维生素 C;paragraph:6", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_007", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子的水分含量较高，吃起来多汁、清爽。", "citation_locator": "line:27;section:2.2 水分;paragraph:7", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_008", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "天气炎热或口渴时，橙子是一种比较适合的水果。", "citation_locator": "line:27;section:2.2 水分;paragraph:7", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_009", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "水果不能完全替代饮水，日常仍然应该保证足够的白水摄入。", "citation_locator": "line:29;section:2.2 水分;paragraph:8", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_010", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子的果肉和白色橘络中含有一定膳食纤维。", "citation_locator": "line:33;section:2.3 膳食纤维;paragraph:9", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_011", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "直接吃完整橙子通常比单纯喝橙汁更有饱腹感，也能保留更多纤维。", "citation_locator": "line:33;section:2.3 膳食纤维;paragraph:9", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_012", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "不同橙子的甜度、酸度、汁水和口感存在差异。", "citation_locator": "line:37;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_013", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "脐橙果肉饱满，甜度较高，酸味适中，适合直接食用。", "citation_locator": "line:41;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_014", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "血橙果肉颜色偏红，风味较特别，适合直接食用和榨汁。", "citation_locator": "line:42;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_015", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "冰糖橙甜味明显，酸味较弱，适合直接食用。", "citation_locator": "line:43;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_016", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "夏橙成熟期较晚，酸甜清爽，适合直接食用和榨汁。", "citation_locator": "line:44;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_017", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "甜橙香气明显，汁水较多，适合榨汁和制作饮品。", "citation_locator": "line:45;section:3. 常见橙子类型;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_018", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子适合在饭后、下午加餐或运动后适量食用。", "citation_locator": "line:49;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:12", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_019", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子味道清爽，可以帮助丰富日常水果种类。", "citation_locator": "line:49;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:12", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_020", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "推荐的吃法包括：剥皮后直接食用；切片加入水果拼盘；榨成果汁但不建议过滤掉全部果肉；与酸奶、坚果搭配；用橙皮少量增加甜点或茶饮香气；做成橙子沙拉、橙汁鸡胸肉等菜品。", "citation_locator": "line:53;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:14", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_021", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "直接吃橙子通常比喝橙汁更推荐，因为榨汁后容易一次摄入多个橙子的糖分，同时膳食纤维会减少。", "citation_locator": "line:60;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:15", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_022", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子相对容易保存，但保存环境会影响口感和新鲜度。", "citation_locator": "line:64;section:5. 保存方法;paragraph:16", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_023", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "短时间内食用的橙子可以放在阴凉通风处，避免阳光直射和潮湿环境。", "citation_locator": "line:68;section:5.1 常温保存;paragraph:17", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_024", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "如果购买数量较多，可以放入冰箱冷藏，可以延长保存时间，保持较好的汁水和口感。", "citation_locator": "line:72;section:5.2 冷藏保存;paragraph:18", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_025", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子表皮如果出现破损，容易加快变质，保存前应先挑出破损、变软或有霉点的橙子。", "citation_locator": "line:76;section:5.3 避免破损;paragraph:19", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_026", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子适合大多数人群食用，尤其适合希望增加水果摄入、补充维生素 C 的人群。", "citation_locator": "line:80;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:20", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_027", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "胃酸较多或胃部不适时，不建议空腹大量吃橙子。", "citation_locator": "line:84;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:22", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_028", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "牙齿敏感的人，吃完较酸的橙子后可以适当漱口。", "citation_locator": "line:85;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:22", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_029", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "血糖控制要求较高的人，应注意摄入量，尤其不建议大量喝橙汁。", "citation_locator": "line:86;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:22", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_030", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子发霉、变味或果肉明显腐烂时，不应继续食用。", "citation_locator": "line:87;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:22", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_031", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "橙子是一种典型的柑橘类水果，最大的特点是酸甜多汁、富含维生素 C、食用方式多样。", "citation_locator": "line:91;section:7. 简要总结;paragraph:23", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_032", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "对于普通人来说，橙子可以作为日常水果的重要选择之一。", "citation_locator": "line:91;section:7. 简要总结;paragraph:23", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_d9ea5683f869_llm_033", "source_id": "src_d9ea5683f869", "claim_text": "相比喝橙汁，更推荐直接吃完整橙子，这样可以摄入更多膳食纤维，也更容易控制总摄入量。", "citation_locator": "line:91;section:7. 简要总结;paragraph:23", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:42:26+00:00"}
